ll be passed to this function. It is guaranteed"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that this callback will be called after all data has been transferred with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the total number of bytes copied during the operation."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" file does not exist, then the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notFound"},{"type":"text","text":" error"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is returned, independent on the status of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"destination","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"overwrite"},{"text":" is not specified and the target exists, then","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the error ","type":"text"},{"code":"exists","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is returned.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If trying to overwrite a file over a directory, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isDirectory"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"error is returned. If trying to overwrite a directory with a directory the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"wouldMerge"},{"text":" error is returned.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the source is a directory and the target does not exist, or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"overwrite"},{"type":"text","text":" is specified and the target is a file, then the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"wouldRecurse"},{"text":" error is returned.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you are interested in copying the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/File"},{"text":" object it